{"lemma":"جُرْمِ","slug":"جُرْمِ","root":"ج.ر.م","root_slug":"ج-ر-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ر-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جُرْمِ","root":"جرم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n5589","n5590","n5591"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%85%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to commit crime, felony"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to incite"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to pick (fruit)","examples":[{"text":"جَرَمَ النَّخْلَ","english":"He picked [fruits from] the date palms"},{"text":"جَرَمَ الثَّمَرَ","english":"He picked the fruits"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to pluck meat off a bone"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to criminalize, to make illegal"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to charge with a crime, to declare a criminal"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"crime, sin, wrongdoing","examples":[{"text":"a. 814, Abu Nuwas\nجَفَانِي بِلَا جُرْمٍ إِلَيْهِ ٱجْتَرَمْتُهُ / وَخَلَّفَنِي نِضْوًا خَلِيًّا مِنَ الصَّبْرِ\njafānī bilā jurmin ʔilayhi jtaramtuhu / waḵallafanī niḍwan ḵaliyyan mina ṣ-ṣabri","english":"(please add an English translation of this quotation)"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a thing that incites anger, aggravates, or instigates ill-will"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"body, mass, bulk, volume of a body","examples":[{"text":"وَفِي ٱلْحَالِ، بَعْدَ ضِيقِ تِلْكَ ٱلْأَيَّامِ، تُظْلِمُ ٱلشَّمْسُ، وَٱلْقَمَرُ لَا يُضِيءُ، وَٱلنُّجُومُ تَسْقُطُ مِنَ ٱلسَّمَاءِ، وَٱلْأَجْرَامُ ٱلسَّمَائِيَّةُ تَرْتَجُّ.","english":"the stars will fall from the sky and the heavenly bodies will be shaken."},{"text":"وَلَقَدْ تَرَكْنا الخَيْلَ فِي عَرَصَاتِهَا كَالطَّيْرِ فَوْقَ مَعَالِمِ الأَجْرَامِ"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n5589","headword_ar":"جَرْمٌ","root":"jrm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hot;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Har~N","text_ar":"حَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or [rather]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAr~N","text_ar":"حَارٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SarodN","text_ar":"صَرْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Lth, TA;) a Persian word, (S,) arabicized; (S, K;) originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Garom","text_ar":"گَرْم"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN jaromN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ جَرْمٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A warm land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hot land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a vehemently hot land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juruwmN","text_ar":"جُرُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AHn, TA,) which, applied to countries, or regions, means the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuruwdN","text_ar":"صُرُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A boat"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaworaqN","text_ar":"زَوْرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of El-Yemen;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqiyrapN","text_ar":"نَقِيرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) pl. as above. (K.) [In the dial. of Egypt, The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"largest kind of Egyptian boat used on the Nile for the conveyance of grain and merchandise in general, but used only when the river is high, and also in the coastingtrade, and generally carrying from"},{"kind":"text","text":"5,000"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to"},{"kind":"text","text":"15,000"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bushels of grain."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["S","AHn","TA","IDrd","K"]},{"entry_id":"n5590","headword_ar":"جُرْمٌ","root":"jrm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sin, a crime, a fault, an offence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an act of disobedience,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*anobN","text_ar":"ذَنْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, * K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether intentional or committed through inadvertence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kull voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ivomN","text_ar":"اـِثْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jariymapN","text_ar":"جَرِيمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarimapN","text_ar":"جَرِمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"transgression:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajoraAmN","text_ar":"اَجْرَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juruwmN","text_ar":"جُرُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) both of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juromN","text_ar":"جُرْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jariyampN","text_ar":"جَرِيَمةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraAy^imu","text_ar":"جَرَايِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraAmN","text_ar":"جَرَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA juroma","text_ar":"لَا جُرْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA jarama","text_ar":"لَا جَرَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n5591","headword_ar":"جِرْمٌ","root":"jrm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"body;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jasadN","text_ar":"جَسَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, K;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badanN","text_ar":"بَدَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Th, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiromaAnN","text_ar":"جِرْمَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^alowaAHi","text_ar":"اَلْوَاحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lawoH","text_ar":"لَوْح"},{"kind":"text","text":"q. v.] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juvomaAn","text_ar":"جُثْمَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jasad","text_ar":"جَسَد"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, TA:) pl. (of pauc., TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^joraAmN","text_ar":"اجْرَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) which is also used as a sing., (TA,) and (of mult., TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juruwmN","text_ar":"جُرُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jurumN","text_ar":"جُرُمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloqaY Ealayohi A^ajoraAmahu","text_ar":"اَلْقَى عَلَيْهِ اَجْرَامَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a phrase mentioned, but not explained, by Lh: ISd thinks that it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He threw upon him the weight of his body;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though the term"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiromN","text_ar":"جِرْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to each separate part of his body. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^ajoraAmu Alfalakiy~apu","text_ar":"الاَجْرَامُ الفَلَكِيَّةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heavenly"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bodies that are above the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EanaASir","text_ar":"عَنَاصِر"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the orbs and stars."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KT.)       -A2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"throat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fauces;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloqN","text_ar":"حَلْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) The phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaDiyqu bihi Aljiromu","text_ar":"يَضِيقُ بِهِ الجِرْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", used by the poet Maan Ibn-'Ows, means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It is a great,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"formidable, thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"matter:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[properly,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the throat"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaloqu","text_ar":"الحَلْقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"will not easily swallow it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"voice;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) mentioned by ISk and others; (S;) and so explained as used in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a fulaAnFA laHasanu Aljiromi","text_ar":"اـِنَّ فُلَانًا لَحَسَنُ الجِرْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily such a one is good in respect of voice"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"highness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loudness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the voice: (K, TA:) you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Earafotuhu A_il~aA","text_ar":"مَا عَرَفْتُهُ اـِلَّا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bijiromihi","text_ar":"بِجِرْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I knew him not save by his voice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his highness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loudness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of voice]: but some disapprove this: (TA:) AHát says that the vulgar are addicted to saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN SaAfiY Aljiromi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ صَافِى الجِرْمِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is clear in voice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in throat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but it is a mistake. (S, TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Colour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, S, Msb, K.) One may say, of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najaAsap","text_ar":"نَجَاسَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or filth],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA jiroma lahaA","text_ar":"لَا جِرْمَ لَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It has no colour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^ajoraAmu","text_ar":"الاَجْرَامُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(app. as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiromN","text_ar":"جِرْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The utensils,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apparatus, of the pastor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","T","TA","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}